Achievements.Name: Founder's travels
Achievements.Description: The founder came on a ship, spotting fertile land.

Achievements.Name: Founder's landing
Achievements.Description: By her command, the people made it theirs.

Achievements.Name: Founder's settling
Achievements.Description: She laid the roots of her greatest masterpiece.

Achievements.Name: Faithfull disciples
Achievements.Description: Four wise disciples gathered under her word.

Achievements.Name: Faithfull Michlan and Xinu
Achievements.Description: Michlan loved death and life, and Xinu loved future and past.

Achievements.Name: Faithfull Chal and Tlaloc
Achievements.Description: Chal and Tlaloc loved rain, sun and sky, and each other even more.

Achievements.Name: The blue fruit
Achievements.Description: Then at last the founders' work bore fruit, and in that she had great hope.

Achievements.Name: The blue boon
Achievements.Description: Trough the essence blue, it might grant endless life.

Achievements.Name: The blue bane
Achievements.Description: But the truth of his boon, was yet to be revealed.

Achievements.Name: Changing mind
Achievements.Description: In time, her mind grew powerfull, but her thoughts grew dark and grim.

Achievements.Name: Changing ruler
Achievements.Description: The keeper of time, her most trusted one, was appointed in her stead.

Achievements.Name: Changing rule
Achievements.Description: Xinu ruled as best he could, and the people flourished.

Achievements.Name: Spreading dissent
Achievements.Description: Of the diciples, one felt that his counsel was much overlooked.

Achievements.Name: Spreading eternity
Achievements.Description: And he gave the diciples the fruits from the founder's tree.

Achievements.Name: Spreading dispair
Achievements.Description: Alone on his throne, Xinu now felt despair descend.

Achievements.Name: Contemplate future
Achievements.Description: He worried for the future, what was to be his final fate?

Achievements.Name: See future
Achievements.Description: A lens he crafted, to see the threads of times unfold.

Achievements.Name: Dread future
Achievements.Description: Trough the lens, Xinu saw only ruin and despair.

Achievements.Name: Xinu's Plea
Achievements.Description: He brought his vision to the founder, and pleaded for her to return.

Achievements.Name: Xinu's labour
Achievements.Description: Together they toiled, attempting to change their people's fate.

Achievements.Name: Xinu's fall
Achievements.Description: The land became neglected as the great task commenced.

Achievements.Name: Empire's decline
Achievements.Description: Their beloved people fell by the wayside, forgotten.

Achievements.Name: Empire's ruin
Achievements.Description: Michlan's most dreaded vision was now complete.

Achievements.Name: Empire's revolt
Achievements.Description: Michlan, Chal and Tlaloc moved to cast Xinu from his throne.

Achievements.Name: Sudden flight
Achievements.Description: The founder fled in the chaos, never seen again.

Achievements.Name: Sudden death
Achievements.Description: Michlan, in his anger, struck Xinu down, his endless life now ended.

Achievements.Name: Sudden fury
Achievements.Description: Horrified at the brutiality, Chal and Tlaloc railed.

Achievements.Name: Michlan's sin
Achievements.Description: Chal was shocked by Michlans action, and she bade Tlaloc act.

Achievements.Name: Michlan's bane
Achievements.Description: They had the people take Michlan, and punish him for his deed.

Achievements.Name: Michlan's fate
Achievements.Description: So Michlan rotted in the dark, while Chal and Tlaloc ruled.

Achievements.Name: Tlaloc's festering
Achievements.Description: But Tlaloc's mind grew dark, and the people's gifts would please him no more.

Achievements.Name: Tlaloc's wrath
Achievements.Description: For long dark years he would use his might to make his wrath known.

Achievements.Name: Chal's voice
Achievements.Description: No single word from Chal would end Tlaloc's terrilbe reign.

Achievements.Name: Chal's flood
Achievements.Description: In the end, Chal would call down the sky to end the blue fruits cycle.

Achievements.Name: Chal's end
Achievements.Description: And so the world ended. Just a handfull were left to start the world anew.

Achievements.Name: Tlaloc's rule
Achievements.Description: Through their power, Chal and Tlaloc gave bounty to the land.

Achievements.Name: Omniscient
Achievements.Description: To see the future clear at last, first you gather all the past.
